1 0 0 1 50 792 Tm (KSS ADMIN GUIDE: HOW TO USE THE INCIDENTS PAGE) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 778 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 764 Tm (PURPOSE) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 750 Tm (This guide is for **KSS Admin users** \(not platform admins\) and explains:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 736 Tm (1. How to add a new incident.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 722 Tm (2. How to update an existing incident.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 708 Tm (3. What each field means and what to check before saving.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 694 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 680 Tm (---) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 666 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 652 Tm (1\) BEFORE YOU START) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 638 Tm (? Make sure you are logged in to KSS.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 624 Tm (? Open **Incidents** from the main navigation.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 610 Tm (? You should be able to see:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 596 Tm (  - The incidents list/table.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 582 Tm (  - Search and filter options.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 568 Tm (  - A **New Incident** button.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 554 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 540 Tm (If you cannot see the Incidents page or button, contact your system owner to confirm your) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 526 Tm (access level.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 512 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 498 Tm (---) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 484 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 470 Tm (2\) ADD A NEW INCIDENT \(STEP-BY-STEP\)) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 456 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 442 Tm (1. Go to **Incidents**.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 428 Tm (2. Click **New Incident**.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 414 Tm (3. Complete the form:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 400 Tm (   - **Store***: Select the affected store.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 386 Tm (   - **Category***: Choose the incident type \(e.g. Accident, Near Miss, Security, Fire,) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 372 Tm (Health & Safety, Other\).) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 358 Tm (   - **Severity***: Low / Medium / High / Critical.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 344 Tm (   - **Summary***: Short, clear incident headline.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 330 Tm (   - **Description**: Full narrative of what happened.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 316 Tm (   - **Occurred At***: Date and time of the event.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 302 Tm (4. Click **Create Incident**.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 288 Tm (5. The system opens the incident detail page automatically.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 274 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 260 Tm (TIPS FOR BETTER INCIDENT QUALITY) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 246 Tm (? Keep the summary factual and short.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 232 Tm (? Put detail in the description \(who, what, where, when, immediate actions\).) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 218 Tm (? Check date/time carefully before submitting.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 204 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 190 Tm (---) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 176 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 162 Tm (3\) UPDATE AN EXISTING INCIDENT \(STEP-BY-STEP\)) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 148 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 134 Tm (1. Open **Incidents**.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 120 Tm (2. Locate the incident \(use search/filters if needed\).) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 106 Tm (3. Click the incident row/card to open it.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 92 Tm (4. On the incident detail page, click **Edit Incident**.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 78 Tm (5. Update fields as needed:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 64 Tm (   - **Category**) Tj
ET
endstream
endobj
