1 0 0 1 50 792 Tm (   - **Severity**) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 778 Tm (   - **Status** \(Open / Under Investigation / Actions In Progress\)) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 764 Tm (   - **Summary**) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 750 Tm (   - **Description**) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 736 Tm (   - **Occurred At**) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 722 Tm (   - **Target Close Date**) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 708 Tm (   - **RIDDOR Reportable** \(Yes/No\)) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 694 Tm (   - Optional JSON sections \(only for advanced users\):) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 680 Tm (     - Persons Involved) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 666 Tm (     - Injury Details) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 652 Tm (     - Witness Statements) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 638 Tm (6. Click **Save Changes**.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 624 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 610 Tm (IMPORTANT NOTES) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 596 Tm (? Keep status aligned with the real case stage.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 582 Tm (? Use **Under Investigation** when review is active.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 568 Tm (? Use **Actions In Progress** when corrective actions are underway.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 554 Tm (? Avoid editing JSON fields unless you are comfortable with valid JSON format.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 540 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 526 Tm (---) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 512 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 498 Tm (4\) ASSIGN AN INVESTIGATOR \(RECOMMENDED WORKFLOW\)) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 484 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 470 Tm (1. Open the incident detail page.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 456 Tm (2. In the investigation area, assign an investigator.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 442 Tm (3. Save/confirm assignment.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 428 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 414 Tm (Tip: assigning an investigator helps ownership and follow-up.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 400 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 386 Tm (---) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 372 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 358 Tm (5\) CLOSE AN INCIDENT) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 344 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 330 Tm (1. Open the incident detail page.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 316 Tm (2. Confirm all required actions/investigation outcomes are completed.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 302 Tm (3. Click **Close Incident** and confirm.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 288 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 274 Tm (Once closed, the incident is moved to the closed incidents area and is treated as) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 260 Tm (historical.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 246 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 232 Tm (---) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 218 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 204 Tm (6\) COMMON MISTAKES TO AVOID) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 190 Tm (? Missing or vague summary text.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 176 Tm (? Wrong incident date/time.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 162 Tm (? Incorrect severity level.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 148 Tm (? Leaving status as Open when investigation has started.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 134 Tm (? Invalid JSON in advanced fields.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 120 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 106 Tm (---) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 92 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 78 Tm (7\) SUGGESTED EMAIL TEXT \(COPY/PASTE\)) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 64 Tm () Tj
